In  40.59(c), in the context of the discussion of the log book, the rule requires the notation of the ``quantified
test result.'' The Department intends that this result be the numerical result displayed by the EBT. The term has the
same meaning as the term ``result displayed on the EBT'' elsewhere in the rule (e.g.,  40.63(d)(1)(i)), and
